<title type="html"><![CDATA[More customization options Classic Shell]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=7705&amp;p=33129#p33129"><![CDATA[
My suggestions for implementation<br /><ol style="list-style-type: decimal"><li>Change the appearance of the avatar frame between the square and round stylized for Windows 10 and larger avatar frame</li><li>Larger icons for items on the right side of the menu</li><li>Icons on the left for the right-hand side menu names</li><li>More predefined start buttons</li><li>Ability to add your own shortcuts, location to the right of the menu</li><li>You can add a command line to the right of the menu</li><li>Possibility to change submenu to dark style</li><li>Can set the same color and transparency instead of the white menu page</li><li>Sort the Applications folder by name just like regular folders in the menu</li><li>You can choose whether to use Modern UI applications in the Applications folder or as shortcuts</li></ol><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=21015">Bladius2018</a> — Sat Jun 24, 2017 12:16 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
